{"tid":1539090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撤回姐係退縮 發夢見到狗落荒而逃應該點呀？","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:00:00.000Z","uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd5d31786cbf68d0ccd32da690379f06efc4d75","tid":1539090,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:49:37.000Z","msg":"晚清改革，又稱庚子新政、庚子後新政，是因1900年（庚子年）義和團與八國聯軍亂後，慈禧太后為反省縱容義和團與八國聯軍之亂，而展開的第三波的政治變革（之後中華民國稱其為「遮羞變法」，香港稱晚清改革，日本稱光緒新政）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%B8%85%E6%9C%AB%E6%96%B0%E6%94%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%259C%25AB%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcanyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=166a0788\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E6%B8%85%E6%9C%AB%E6%96%B0%E6%94%BF</a>"},{"pid":"c1784040e9186d721b59dfc432e294885b0edf99","tid":1539090,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:00:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 應承我！<br />\n一日未答應五大訴求 都要繼續上街</span></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2P